<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 14:07:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列南部被警察枪杀的贝都因妇女称自己无缘无故被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-woman-shot-by-police-officer-in-southern-israel-says-she-was-shot-for-no-reason/0000018f-8b12-ded1-a7df-df520b880000</link><description>伊塔布·阿萨娜 (Itab A-Sana) 的腿部被一名前来搜寻她儿子的警察开枪射中，她的儿子目前正在接受审讯。警方称，这名警官向一只狗开枪，他认为这只狗构成危险，阿萨娜受伤后，警方呼吁医疗救助</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 13:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-woman-shot-by-police-officer-in-southern-israel-says-she-was-shot-for-no-reason/0000018f-8b12-ded1-a7df-df520b880000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前议员、自由派偶像雅埃尔·达扬 (Yael Dayan) 去世，享年 85 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/yael-dayan-former-israeli-lawmaker-and-liberal-icon-dies-at-85/0000018e-c3ab-dc93-adce-effbd4580000</link><description>达扬 (Dayan) 于 1992 年至 2003 年间担任以色列议会议员，是一位著名的人权活动家，关注妇女和 LGBTQ 群体的问题。近年来，她患有严重的肺部疾病</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 12:20:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/yael-dayan-former-israeli-lawmaker-and-liberal-icon-dies-at-85/0000018e-c3ab-dc93-adce-effbd4580000</guid></item><item><title>第一批救援卡车通过新开放的浮动码头进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/first-convoy-of-aid-trucks-cross-into-gaza-via-newly-opened-floating-pier/0000018f-8b1e-d6b6-a59f-fb9fb4bc0000</link><description>美国官员预计该行动每天将运送 150 卡车的援助物资，然后由联合国世界粮食计划署收集和分发</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 11:49:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/first-convoy-of-aid-trucks-cross-into-gaza-via-newly-opened-floating-pier/0000018f-8b1e-d6b6-a59f-fb9fb4bc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议员纳马·拉齐米并不害怕内塔尼亚胡和本·格维尔。她会带回犹太复国主义左派吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-and-ben-gvir-dont-scare-israeli-mk-naama-lazimi-can-she-save-the-zionist-left/0000018f-8649-d7ca-afcf-97eb622d0000</link><description>近几个月来，工党议员纳马·拉齐米 (Naama Lazimi) 一直是反政府抗议活动前线的重要人物，与人质家属并肩作战，争取亲人从加沙返回。她说：“我是议会反对党成员，我有责任尽我所能控制警察并团结一致。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 10:28:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-and-ben-gvir-dont-scare-israeli-mk-naama-lazimi-can-she-save-the-zionist-left/0000018f-8649-d7ca-afcf-97eb622d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军和辛贝特在加沙地带找到了哈马斯扣押的三名以色列人质的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/idf-retrieves-bodies-of-three-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018f-875c-d7f9-a5ff-b77eecc40000</link><description>沙尼·洛克、阿米特·布斯基拉和伊扎克·格勒伦特都被新星狂欢节劫持为人质。据以色列国防军称，三人从狂欢场跑到梅法西姆交界处，在那里被哈马斯恐怖分子谋杀，尸体被带入加沙</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 08:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/idf-retrieves-bodies-of-three-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018f-875c-d7f9-a5ff-b77eecc40000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯犹太运动“站在一起”计划保护加沙援助车队免受右翼掠夺者的侵害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/arab-jewish-movement-standing-together-to-guard-gaza-aid-convoys-from-right-wing-looters/0000018f-8a88-d9d6-a38f-8ffb2bc10000</link><description>为了抵制右翼活动人士阻止援助卡车抵达加沙的努力，“站在一起”计划建立一个缓冲区，并希望警方帮助维持和平</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 08:13:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/arab-jewish-movement-standing-together-to-guard-gaza-aid-convoys-from-right-wing-looters/0000018f-8a88-d9d6-a38f-8ffb2bc10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列可能会跌倒并再次崛起</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israel-may-fall-and-rise-again/0000018f-89d3-d7f4-adbf-a9ff75c10000</link><description>那些谈论以色列灭亡的人可以分为两类：希望以色列灭亡的人和害怕以色列灭亡的人。以色列人未来可能会失去主权——但这可能不是我们想象的噩梦</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 04:12:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israel-may-fall-and-rise-again/0000018f-89d3-d7f4-adbf-a9ff75c10000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸的 18 个巴勒斯坦牧羊社区最近被消灭。这个可能是下一个</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/18-west-bank-shepherding-communities-have-been-recently-erased-this-one-might-be-next/0000018f-83c5-d9d6-a38f-87ff376b0000</link><description>定居者多年来一直骚扰杰里科附近的一个贝都因小村庄，但在战争期间，他们加大了恐吓力度。身着军服、配备军车的大屠杀分子夺取了该地区的土地，并建立了 13 个新的前哨基地——这一切都是从 10 月份开始的</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 03:50:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/18-west-bank-shepherding-communities-have-been-recently-erased-this-one-might-be-next/0000018f-83c5-d9d6-a38f-87ff376b0000</guid></item><item><title>“犯罪组织正在控制以色列的阿拉伯社会。他们也是为了犹太社会而来”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/crime-orgs-are-controlling-israels-arab-society-theyre-coming-for-jewish-society-too/0000018f-8990-d9d6-a38f-8dfb38780000</link><description>Rawyah Handaqlu 是一个紧急机构的负责人，该机构的成立是为了应对席卷阿拉伯社会的犯罪和暴力浪潮，他谈论了生活在一个犯罪组织取代国家的社会中的感受</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 03:27:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/crime-orgs-are-controlling-israels-arab-society-theyre-coming-for-jewish-society-too/0000018f-8990-d9d6-a38f-8dfb38780000</guid></item><item><title>“我们的鲜血只适合战争”：在加沙作战，他们感到平等。回到以色列的家，这种感觉破碎了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/fighting-in-gaza-they-feel-equal-back-home-in-israel-that-feeling-is-shattered/0000018f-870e-d443-adef-9fce5c9d0000</link><description>在加沙服役和阵亡的以色列士兵中有相当多的埃塞俄比亚人后裔。有些人认为战争已经成为进入以色列社会的一种门票——但代价是什么？</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 02:36:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/fighting-in-gaza-they-feel-equal-back-home-in-israel-that-feeling-is-shattered/0000018f-870e-d443-adef-9fce5c9d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称从加沙北部向以色列南部发射了 10 枚火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-live/israeli-air-force-strikes-building-in-west-bank-wanted-terrorist-killed/0000018f-8960-d9d6-a38f-8dfb3ff10000</link><description>外国消息人士称人质谈判陷入僵局 ■ 第一批人道主义援助物资通过美国新码头抵达加沙 ■ 以色列军队连夜对约旦河西岸城市杰宁进行空袭 ■ 以色列国防军：以色列国防军从加沙打捞出三名人质的尸体</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 02:10:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-live/israeli-air-force-strikes-building-in-west-bank-wanted-terrorist-killed/0000018f-8960-d9d6-a38f-8dfb3ff10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列空军袭击约旦河西岸的建筑物；击毙通缉恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-air-force-strikes-building-in-west-bank-kills-wanted-terrorist/0000018f-88b3-d9d6-a38f-8dfb69480000</link><description>据以色列军方称，目标建筑被用作作战作战室</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 22:56:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-air-force-strikes-building-in-west-bank-kills-wanted-terrorist/0000018f-88b3-d9d6-a38f-8dfb69480000</guid></item><item><title>加州大学武装警察与亲巴勒斯坦抗议者发生暴力冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/armed-police-clash-violently-with-pro-palestinian-protesters-at-california-university/0000018f-8898-d9d6-a38f-8dfbee7e0000</link><description>加州大学欧文分校的亲巴勒斯坦营地占领了一座空置建筑，导致警方采取严厉措施，近 50 人被捕</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 22:33:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/armed-police-clash-violently-with-pro-palestinian-protesters-at-california-university/0000018f-8898-d9d6-a38f-8dfbee7e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名在加沙北部战斗中阵亡的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-soldier-killed-in-combat-in-northern-gaza/0000018f-8841-d6b6-a59f-facbb18e0000</link><description>中士。 20 岁的本·阿维沙伊 (Ben Avishay) 来自以色列北部城市纳哈里亚 (Nahariya)，在贾巴利亚 (Jabalya) 与恐怖分子的对抗中身亡。他是自10月7日以来第628名阵亡士兵</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 20:59:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-soldier-killed-in-combat-in-northern-gaza/0000018f-8841-d6b6-a59f-facbb18e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 224 天：大约 75 枚火箭从黎巴嫩向以色列戈兰高地发射</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-224-some-75-rockets-fired-at-israels-golan-heights-from-lebanon/0000018f-8759-d7ca-afcf-97fb75770001</link><description>以色列国防军表示，他们在加沙找到了 10 月 7 日被哈马斯扣为人质的三名以色列人的尸体。 ■ 以色列向国际法院陈述案情。 ■ 中央司令部：第一批运载援助物资的卡车穿过新建的美国码头进入加沙。 ■ 约 75 枚火箭弹从黎巴嫩发射到以色列戈兰高地高地 ■ 以色列极右活动分子袭击了他们以为正在向加沙运送援助物资的阿拉伯裔以色列卡车司机 ■ 战争进入 224 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 16:37:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-224-some-75-rockets-fired-at-israels-golan-heights-from-lebanon/0000018f-8759-d7ca-afcf-97fb75770001</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：向以色列北部发射了 75 枚火箭弹；报告：真主党高级指挥官被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-75-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-report-senior-hezbollah-commander-killed/0000018f-8712-d7ca-afcf-97fb78cc0000</link><description>以色列北部社区的两人受轻伤，一所房屋受损</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 15:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-75-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-report-senior-hezbollah-commander-killed/0000018f-8712-d7ca-afcf-97fb78cc0000</guid></item><item><title>出于想法，内塔尼亚胡将拜登和国防部长加兰特视为密谋反对他的阴谋集团</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/out-of-ideas-netanyahu-sees-biden-and-gallant-as-a-cabal-plotting-against-him/0000018f-8663-d443-adef-9febbcf20000</link><description>加沙战争正在变得像1982年开始的黎巴嫩泥潭一样，带有美国在越南失败的味道。但以色列仍然没有战后计划</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 14:30:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/out-of-ideas-netanyahu-sees-biden-and-gallant-as-a-cabal-plotting-against-him/0000018f-8663-d443-adef-9febbcf20000</guid></item><item><title>据《华盛顿邮报》报道，以色列军队似乎正在利用加沙医院、学校作为基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/israeli-army-appears-to-be-using-gaza-hospital-school-as-bases-washington-post-reports/0000018f-868c-d443-adef-9fcc60e20000</link><description>卫星图像显示 11 月在土耳其-巴勒斯坦友谊医院周围以及 3 月在 Juhor ad Dik 学校附近修建土堤。上个月，《国土报》发布了卫星图像，显示以色列国防军部队集中在附近的内扎里姆走廊沿线。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 13:43:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/israeli-army-appears-to-be-using-gaza-hospital-school-as-bases-washington-post-reports/0000018f-868c-d443-adef-9fcc60e20000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争是悲惨的，但没有发生种族灭绝：以色列在国际法庭上陈述案情</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/war-in-gaza-tragic-but-no-genocide-taking-place-israel-presents-its-case-at-world-court/0000018f-85ef-d7f9-a5ff-b5ff9a610000</link><description>以色列提出论点，要求国际法院驳回南非停止在拉法行动并从加沙地带撤军的请求。预计下周将就紧急措施请求做出决定</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 11:11:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/war-in-gaza-tragic-but-no-genocide-taking-place-israel-presents-its-case-at-world-court/0000018f-85ef-d7f9-a5ff-b5ff9a610000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在对他来说唯一重要的战争中占据上风：保持权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-the-upper-hand-in-the-only-war-that-matters-to-him-staying-in-power/0000018f-82a7-d7f9-a5ff-b7f725d80000</link><description>任何声称以色列总理没有战略的人都是错误的：他认为政治生存高于一切 ■ 一句随口的话如何概括了以色列处理加沙战争的悲剧 ■ 总理策划了他的“全面胜利”之路到十月</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 03:00:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-the-upper-hand-in-the-only-war-that-matters-to-him-staying-in-power/0000018f-82a7-d7f9-a5ff-b7f725d80000</guid></item></channel></rss>